、俄羅斯及中國大陸。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af54fb58f072130295637707f5dacb9e876b32b7","tid":2490362,"uid":66087,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:08:50.000Z","msg":"今晚講緊，美國國勢大收縮開始中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6950905af1029f7dc19aa54405ed08b81a3c6d7b","tid":2490362,"uid":59976,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:09:41.000Z","msg":"撤得支那就好心撒埋香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914fcec248dc3606bb03301f165b5d86867ea596","tid":2490362,"uid":149494,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af54fb58f072130295637707f5dacb9e876b32b7","tid":2490362,"uid":66087,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:08:50.000Z","msg":"今晚講緊，美國國勢大收縮開始中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:11:07.000Z","msg":"你聽緊乜咁撚on9?"},{"pid":"d35959224ba3f4fef41cc7b6585468c36f888cc8","tid":2490362,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:13:01.000Z","msg":"人生太短出手要更大"},{"pid":"68bcd2b0759bc241375c02bf25889300c86136f7","tid":2490362,"uid":51665,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:13:19.000Z","msg":"中國大陸＝香港<br />\n尾國早巳認證一國一制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc76812c9639aaa973b82765e3139d29e47f459","tid":2490362,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"h