91b59100c8c6134c7","tid":2490362,"uid":64345,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:17:16.000Z","msg":"等睇香港人由花旗搬返啲錢返去匯豐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:22:13.000Z","msg":"真係撐邊樣邊樣就死"},{"pid":"cc6bbe8fcf57f7c7a3bc511144da527185fc2431","tid":2490362,"uid":46356,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:23:53.000Z","msg":"真係唔包香港<br />\n反而係強化香港業務<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1618490356152&amp;issue=20210415\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1618490356152%26issue%3D20210415&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=893162ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1618490356152&amp;issue=20210415</a><br />\n<br />\n花旗退出13個地區 唯承諾香港仍是關鍵市場<br />\n文章日期：2021年4月15日 20:34<br />\n<br />\n花旗銀行今晚公布首季業績的同時，宣布退出13個亞洲及歐洲地區的零售業務，包括中國、澳洲、印度、印尼、韓國、馬來西亞、菲律賓、台灣、巴林、泰國、越南、俄羅斯及波蘭。<span class=\"red\">集團表示，計劃專注於香港、新加坡、阿聯酋及倫敦</span>。<br />\n<br />\n花旗集團香港及澳門區行政總裁伍燕儀表示，香港是花旗集團的關鍵戰略市場，而集團的香港業務則為花旗集團全球收入最大的貢獻者之一，集團將繼續投放資源以服務客戶。花旗集團在香港擁有悠久的歷史，對香港市場的未來充滿信心，並將繼續支持香港客戶及與客戶一起成長。"},{"pid":"20464acbf296f15e59be9b63026f169cbdb00f55","tid":2490362,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2ebec61bf328db11d9b038f813ac5be42a62f4","tid":2490362,"uid":188282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af54fb58f072130295637707f5dacb9e876b32b7","tid":2490362,"uid":66087,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:08:50.000Z","msg":"今晚講緊，美國國勢大收縮開始中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:25:55.000Z","msg":"亞洲打仗<br />\n支滅"},{"pid":"af8c0e7653ddc0db685e6d54254369630ee24e24","tid":2490362,"uid":189374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:26:57.000Z","msg":"今個月BEST TRADE : <br />\nHDB<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910d18db323a6493062844c9fc8f6730c05481c3","tid":2490362,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af54fb58f072130295637707f5dacb9e876b32b7","tid":2490362,"uid":66087,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:08:50.000Z","msg":"今晚講緊，美國國勢大收縮開始中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:27:37.000Z","msg":"亞洲打仗<br />\n支滅"}]}